CREATE TABLE circuits (
numbers_0 integer,
racecircuits_1 text,
race_circuits_2 text,
race_locations_3 text,
countries_4 text,
values_list_5 real,
values_list_6 real,
null_values_7 integer,
race_circuits_8 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE constructors (
numbers_0 integer,
teams_1 text,
teams_2 text,
nationalities_3 text,
f1_teams_wiki_links_4 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE drivers (
numbers_0 integer,
drivers_1 text,
column_2_2 integer,
words_list_3 text,
drivers_4 text,
drivers_5 text,
dates_6 date,
nationalities_7 text,
drivers_wiki_links_8 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE seasons (
years_0 integer,
f1_seasons_1 text,
PRIMARY KEY (years_0),
);
CREATE TABLE races (
numbers_0 integer,
years_1 integer,
numbers_list_2 integer,
column_3_3 integer,
gp_races_4 text,
dates_5 date,
time_slots_6 text,
race_urls_7 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (years_1) REFERENCES seasons(years_0),
FOREIGN KEY (column_3_3) REFERENCES circuits(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE constructorResults (
numbers_0 integer,
ages_1 integer,
numbers_list_2 integer,
values_list_3 real,
null_values_4 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (ages_1) REFERENCES races(numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (numbers_list_2) REFERENCES constructors(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE constructorStandings (
numbers_0 integer,
age_1 integer,
column_2_2 integer,
values_list_3 real,
column_4_4 integer,
item_ids_5 text,
binary_flags_6 integer,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (age_1) REFERENCES races(numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (column_2_2) REFERENCES constructors(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE driverStandings (
numbers_0 integer,
age_1 integer,
numbers_list_2 integer,
values_list_3 real,
column_4_4 integer,
numbers_5 text,
binary_flags_6 integer,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (age_1) REFERENCES races(numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (numbers_list_2) REFERENCES drivers(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE lapTimes (
ones_0 integer,
ones_1 integer,
numbers_2 integer,
values_3 integer,
times_4 text,
values_list_5 integer,
FOREIGN KEY (ones_0) REFERENCES races(numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (ones_1) REFERENCES drivers(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE pitStops (
value_841_0 integer,
values_1 integer,
sequence_type_2 integer,
ages_3 integer,
timestamp_4 text,
temperatures_5 text,
customer_ids_6 integer,
FOREIGN KEY (value_841_0) REFERENCES races(numbers_0),
FOREIGN KEY (values_1) REFERENCES drivers(numbers_0),
);
CREATE TABLE qualifying (
numbers_0 integer,
value_18_1 integer,
numbers_list_2 integer,
column_3_3 integer,
numbers_list_4 integer,
numbers_5 integer,
times_6 text,
race_time_7 text,
race_time_8 text,
PRIMARY KEY (numbers_0),
